l——都完成了个人项目。平诺克在与华纳唱片公司签约之前， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/leigh-anne-pinnock-praises-very-supportive-little-mix-acting-debut-3113002">在圣诞电影<em>《节礼日》</em>中</a>担任表演角色。</p><p>在为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/twice">TWICE</a> （《First Time》）、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/iggy-azalea">Iggy Azalea</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/britney-spears">Britney Spears</a> （《Pretty Girls》）等<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/twice-working-with-little-mix-jade-thirlwall-very-honoured-2971009">人创作歌曲</a>后，瑟尔沃尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-mixs-jade-thirlwal-to-go-solo-signs-global-record-deal-with-rca-3181300">与 RCA Records 签署了一项全球协议</a>。</p><p>佩里<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/perrie-edwards-reveals-new-solo-album-features-raye-and-ed-sheeran-3600525">·爱德华兹 (Perrie Edwards) 发布了新个人专辑，其中 RAYE 和艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran)</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
